org.jvault.factory.extensible

Interface VaultFactoryBuildInfo

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractVaultFactoryBuildInfo, AnnotationVaultFactoryBuildInfo, PropertiesVaultFactoryBuildInfo

    @ExtensiblePoint
public interface VaultFactoryBuildInfo
    One of the parameters that VaultFactory receives.
    This interface returns the name of the vault to be created,
    location information of beans,
    and package information that can use the vault.
    Since:
    0.1
    Author:
    devxb
    See Also:
    PropertiesVaultFactoryBuildInfo, AbstractVaultFactoryBuildInfo, BeanLocation
